        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "马戏与龙　后篇",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "沉迷马戏的少年和龙\\n向村民们展示了\\n仅由他们带来的马戏表演。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "不论是鲜花盛开的春天，\\n还是阳光炫目的夏天，\\n又或是红叶惹眼的秋天，\\n以及银装素裹的冬天。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "他们坚持不懈地表演马戏，\\n然而某一天，\\n这一切突然迎来了终结。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“今天也来表演马戏吧！”\\n“抱歉，我得给家里帮忙。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_120019_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“今天也来表演马戏吧！”\\n“抱歉，我得去照顾孩子。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_120014_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“今天也不能表演马戏吗？”\\n“抱歉……\\n我的身体已经\\n不像小孩那么灵活了。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_120021_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "孩子总会成长为大人。\\n这一点龙也一样。\\n只是两者成为大人所需的\\n时间差异大得过于残忍。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "在旁人看来，\\n他们已不再是关系亲密的搭档。\\n共同练习技艺的搭档\\n经历了长大、老去，\\n直至最终去世。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "为了填补内心的孤独，\\n龙决心忘记村子、少年\\n和原本带给他\\n无限快乐的马戏。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "尽管如此，\\n他的想法还是根深蒂固。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“想和人类做好玩的事。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "龙衷心希望\\n还能再一次迎来\\n与人类共同度过的欢乐时光。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "然而岁月流逝，\\n龙还是觉得无趣至极，\\n并深深感到了孤独。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“也许再也不会\\n有好玩的事了。”\\n龙像是放弃了一般，叹了口气。\\n就在此时……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“你的表情好阴沉啊。\\n不介意的话，\\n和我一起去看马戏吧？”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "耳边响起了熟悉的话语，\\n眼前出现了熟悉的帐篷。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "龙两眼放光，\\n喜悦的咆哮声响彻云霄。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_210043_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "自那以后，\\n带着龙的少女所在的马戏团\\n让大街小巷热闹了起来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "据说少女和龙\\n今天也在为人们\\n带来欢乐的表演。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "如果对真实性心存疑虑，\\n就去那色彩鲜艳的帐篷里\\n确认一下真相吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "这会儿应该\\n快听到开演的铃声了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}